<br>
I know my question isn't a good one since it calls for too many undefined terms (i.e. Legitimate cause, reasonable suspicion, etc), so once again I am just kind of mulling it over.  I am very aware that this is coming from a lower-middle class white guy who lives in the suburbs... so this may have some impact on my opinion, despite the fact that I am very against racism and prejudism.<br>
