<br>
<br>
<blockquote type=cite><blockquote><hr>The FBI defines hate crimes as "a criminal offense committed against a person, property or society which is motivated, in whole or in part, by the offender's bias against a race, religion, disability, sexual orientatio, or ethnicity/national origin."<hr></blockquote></blockquote><br>
