<br>
<blockquote type=cite><blockquote><hr>""There's a reason for this. These demographics are the minority. The intent is to attempt to protect minorities, to give them the same liberties that the 'majority' holds. The majority may be the Catholics, the Whites, the Heterosexuals, or just the opposite (in my mind) if someone attacks, kills or threatens a person who is in the minority in a situation where the majority could pose a serious hamper on his/her liberty. <br>
